        'Slowly roll up and down, covering entire outer thigh.',
        'Pause on tender spots, breathe deeply.',
        'Control the movement, avoid jerky motions.'
      ],
      common_mistakes: [
        'Rolling too quickly.',
        'Applying too much pressure too soon.',
        'Holding breath due to discomfort.'
